Where The Senior Locals Gather]

335
00:15:55,621 --> 00:15:59,567
[And Share Their Daily Lives]

336
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:03,162
Would you like to head in first?

337
00:16:06,399 --> 00:16:08,901
It's such a pretty bakery.

338
00:16:09,869 --> 00:16:11,603
Gosh, check this out.

339
00:16:13,172 --> 00:16:15,207
Wow, it's so charming.

340
00:16:15,207 --> 00:16:17,476
They did a great job.

341
00:16:17,476 --> 00:16:19,678
It's a fantastic set-up.

342
00:16:19,678 --> 00:16:21,580
Wow, it's gorgeous.

343
00:16:25,351 --> 00:16:27,787
[Village Corner Store]

344
00:16:27,787 --> 00:16:30,923
[Bonjour Bakery]

345
00:16:30,923 --> 00:16:34,881
