346
00:16:36,595 --> 00:16:40,759
[Has Been Reborn]
[As A Space Brimming With Warmth]

347
00:16:46,038 --> 00:16:47,473
[Senior Café]
[Bonjour Bakery]

348
00:16:47,473 --> 00:16:50,209
[Anyone Over 65 Years Old]

349
00:16:50,209 --> 00:16:54,271
[Can Drop In And Visit]

350
00:16:55,648 --> 00:16:58,951
